phan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra侦查</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的"侦查"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D30/80 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >敌人倒下了，不要手下留情。（困难成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:正当你凝视着尸体思索时，它干枯的眼睛突然动了起来，直勾勾地盯着你。紧接着，那张始终挂着微笑的脸喃喃道：“黄衣之王会听取愚者的祈愿。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >然而，在你眨眼的瞬间，尸体便恢复了原状，依然面无表情地向虚空露出微笑。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:sc1/1D3。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.sc1/1D3</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的理智检定:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >d100=3D20/43 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >把你们破坏殆尽</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……降临吧，洛基。（困难成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >理智变化</font>: 43 &#10159; 42 (扣除1=3D1点)</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >因为是侦探所以这种情况对我来说当然不在话下</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……但我没想到你居然也能应付得来这些事呢。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智也可以过个灵感或艺术。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra灵感</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的"灵感"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D68/80 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >不错的一击，保持这个状态继续吧。（成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:回忆起刚刚像幻觉一样的景象我有些想吐。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智意识到，尸体的形态是由三个“？”组成的印记，就像某种纹章。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:这时三上也回到了实验室：“如何，观察得怎么样了？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“总觉得这具尸体让人感到很困惑呢。”我说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“诶？明智君，没事吧？”那种担忧的眼神</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“没事，想到了一件微不足道的小事，这位死者出事的那天是我的生日，真是不巧啊。”我为了缓解氛围，说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“这样啊……”三上大概是不知道如何回答，只好这样接话。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“怎么会这样…那我们赶快把凶手抓住吧！”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“以防万一我想确认一下，尸体死后应该是不会说话的吧？”我试探三上。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“这是当然的。”三上点点头，似乎终于发觉了你不太好的面色，“你还好吗？为了身心健康，我想观察完毕后及时离开是比较好的选择。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“没错，这是常识呢。那么也不可能会说什么‘黄衣之主’之类的了……吧？”我感觉三上似乎没什么波澜，决定放弃。“哈哈……真是不好意思，好久没看到尸体，有些大惊小怪了，真是失态。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“是吗？”三上目光有些怀疑，似乎欲言又止，但最终只是开始收拾实验室内的物品，“如果结束了就离开实验室吧。我送你们回招待处。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“我听田中说你们在追查雨人。如果不介意的话，能告诉我你们追查他的原因吗？雨人……是个会将受害者折磨成那种模样的极端人物。你们在调查过程中，说不定会碰到他。即便如此，为什么你们还要继续呢？这让我有些在意……”她带着路，边询问道。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:。log off 愚者的祈雨</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:“要继续讲述这个故事吗？我很乐意倾听下去。”他看起来倒是很有耐心的样子。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >故事</font>"愚者的祈雨"的记录已经继续开启，当前已记录文本821</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“该怎么回答呢……因为正义吗？有点像小孩才会用的借口呢。”我回答。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:听到三上小姐的话不由得思考了起来。“…我的理由…大概是这是我的工作吧。如果能够调查出雨人的真面目，能够阻止更多的人死去，那么也能证明自己是有用的吧？…感觉这个更像小孩子的理由呢。”有些不好意思地笑了起来。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“铃木君的理由比我更像大人多了。”我夸赞。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“正义和证明自己吗……不，这些都是很有力量的理由呢。”三上思索了一下，露出理解的神情。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >没过多久，你们就到达了接待处。三上将自己的名片递给你们：</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“请一定小心。如果有什么我能帮忙的，随时联系我。”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“谢谢你，三上小姐。”我笑着接过。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:接过名片礼貌地笑了一下。“好的，谢谢你…！”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:名片脱手，三上点点头，与你们告别了。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“那么…接下来只剩下去调查东部地区了吧？在这之前还有什么其他事吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“或许没有了，你想向田中警官先汇报一下也不是不行噢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:不自觉咬了下手指甲，对于跟刑警打交道有着莫名抵触。“这个…反正储存卡也坏了，不如找到据点再一起汇报吧！嗯…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“铃木君真是有干劲呢。好，那我们出发吧。”我笑着说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:加祸市并不大，然而被划作东部的区域也拥有四五十平方公里的面积。区域内居民区、商业区、工业区一应俱全。你们姑且来到了东区的边缘。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:那么就在此时，铃木的手机响了——是来自佐佐木的呼叫。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:慌忙接起。“喂？我是铃木。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“我是佐佐木。铃木，我刚刚整理出了前几次事件受害者的家庭地址，已经发送到你的工作邮箱了。呃，虽然在已经被拒绝的情况下登门采访可能不会有什么好结果……如果你们需要的话，或许可以试试看吧。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“啊，好的佐佐木先生，我了解了。”我捂住话筒偏过头问，“明智君，有什么事要跟佐佐木先生说吗？他说会给我们发送受害者家属的地址。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我摇了摇头。“那就麻烦佐佐木先生了。消息真是太及时了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我试图用电话那头也能听到的声音说。“帮大忙了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“啊哈哈，没有啦。这是我应该做的。”不知装傻成分有多少，总之佐佐木进行了爽朗的回应，“那么就这样。你们调查时一定要小心。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“好的我们会注意的，谢谢您，那么再见了。”进行一个挂电话</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“等事情完结后，一定要让佐佐木先生请我们吃饭呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“那么，我们先来整理一下家属的地址吧？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那么我打开邮箱进行查看</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:如佐佐木所言，铃木的邮箱已经收到了整理好的地址列表。还算幸运的是，一半的地址就在东区，剩下的也距你们的所在地不会太远。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:这些地址旁还附带着联系电话。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“真是太好了，佐佐木先生的消息确实很及时呢。”我的语气听上去很愉悦。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“除去排查据点以外还增加了采访家属呢…不过我相信明智君的魅力能够征服他们呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“啊哈哈，铃木君真是会说话呢，谢谢你的夸奖，不过如果被拒绝的话可不要失望哦？”我拿出了手机。“我们可以称自己是警方的人，有些关于案件细节需要确认。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:。st show 话术</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的个人属性为:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >话术</font>:5</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:。st show 说服</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的个人属性为:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >说服</font>:10</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:。st show 取悦</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的个人属性为:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >取悦</font>:25</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:看了眼铃木紧张的样子，我无奈地笑了笑：“我来打吧。”那么我按照顺序拨打电话，按照准备好的说辞询问受害者家属是否愿意接受走访。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:感激地看了眼明智君，把资料和自己的手机也准备好。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你向第一户打了过去，手机响起了等待音。这声音在你耳畔环绕，直至呼叫时间的最后一刻。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >依照顺序，拨打此后人家的号码。无一例外，无人应答。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“看样子我们不得不登门拜访了呢。”我放下电话，叹了口气。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“总有一种不好的预感…”跟着叹气</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“打起精神来，我们一起出发吧？”我鼓励道。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“先从最近的一家开始……”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“好，那我们就从最近的一家开始！”给自己鼓气</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:那么你们根据佐佐木提供的地址，规划出最佳路线后开始逐一拜访。然而，不知是家中无人，还是遗属们有意回避，在这些地址所对应的房屋，你们的拜访也没能得到回应。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >最后一户是第六位受害者的家，同样无人应答。正当你们打算放弃时，背后传来了女性的声音：</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“请问有什么事吗？”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:一名清瘦的中年女性看着你们。她提着手袋，看上去像刚购物回来。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“你好，我们是加祸市警方派来走访调查的，有关雨人案件或将取得新的进展，请问你是否愿意配合我们呢？”我微笑，礼貌地说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“这样啊……”女性露出温和的笑容，“好吧。你们有什么想询问我的呢？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“谢谢您的配合。我想知道的是，受害者在案件发生前有没有什么奇怪的行动，或者有没有什么新朋友？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“他遇见了雨人。”女性的语气很平淡，“……他是我最重要的孩子。但他现在属于雨人，不再是我的了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“属于……？你和那位雨人有过接触吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“雨人就在这座城市里，现在也在注视着你们。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“他是赋予那孩子永恒的存在。”谈及受害者的死，女性显得有些漠然。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我们想见一见雨人，是否有那种办法存在呢？”我压下内心的不安问。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“我愿意说，会的。如果你们能见到雨人，就好了呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“见到雨人之后…我们也会被赋予永恒的生命吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“当然。成为雨人的东西，就会永远活下去。我感觉自己也快要成为那样的永恒存在了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“那我……可以拒绝雨人的好意吗？”我神色复杂。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:女性垂下眼眸，没有回答。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“如果可以的话，雨人会允许我们见证你成为永恒存在的瞬间吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“这是你所希望的吗？”女性微微侧头，面部看不出表情变化。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那种担心的眼神，虽然不是在问自己但还是摇了摇头</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“哈……”我感觉女人很是诡异，这个问题也不像是适合回答的，倒吸了口气没有回答。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“总之，近期请注意安全。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我思索了一下继续说，“尽量不要远离家的附近。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我低头玩手机把对话的大概内容发送给田中刑警，询问这种情况是否需要派人照看。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:短暂的沉默后，女性转回了头。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >“采访结束了么？”女性轻声道，“那么，我该告辞了。那孩子在等我。”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:说着，她伸手握住玄关的门把手。门轻轻打开的瞬间，一股难以忍受的腐臭从屋内扑面而来，屋内传出无数翅膀拍动的声音。你们不由自主地开始想象屋内的情景。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:sc0/1。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.sc0/1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的理智检定:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >d100=3D99/42 洛基服的明智转过头去，对你刚刚的所作所为发出了一声颇具嘲讽的嗤笑声。（大失败）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >理智变化</font>: 42 &#10159; 41 (扣除1=3D1点)</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >你很快就能洞悉一切</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“啊，对了。要是能见到——”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >女性迈步进屋内，未尽的话语消散在空中。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:.sc0/1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的理智检定:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >d100=3D16/73 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >把你们破坏殆尽</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……降临吧，洛基。（困难成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >理智变化</font>: 73 &#10159; 73 (扣除0=3D0点)</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >因为是侦探所以这种情况对我来说当然不在话下</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……但我没想到你居然也能应付得来这些事呢。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:不祥的感觉，反而使明智产生了一种一探究竟的欲望。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:不一会儿，铃木收到了田中的回复：“她这么说吗？谢谢你，铃木君，我之后来查看情况。你们就先安心回到调查工作中吧。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我拽拽明智君的衣角试图让明智君转移注意力</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我回过神来，控制住了向室内看去的想法。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“明智君，如果说…受害者家属们都是这种情况的话，那岂不是意味着他们都有可能，成为了那什么雨人的东西…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“啊……如果真的是这样的话，那就糟糕了。”我面色凝重。“比起这个，我们继续搜查吧？不过当然了，我们要更加注意安全问题。这起事件很诡异。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:走访了诸多地点后，夕阳的红色已将整座城市笼罩。铃木的手机响起，是佐佐木再一次打来了电话。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:一激灵接了起来。“佐佐木先生。我是铃木。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“铃木君，辛苦了，今天的采访就到此为止吧。能回新闻社一趟吗？”佐佐木的声音顿了顿，“你和明智君是一起采访的吧？如果不是的话我再打电话通知他……”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“啊，是的我们正在一起走访。我会转告他的。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我们是一起采访的噢。佐佐木先生。”我出声回答。“顺便问一句，我今晚该住在哪里呢？我还是未成年噢，晚上在外面逗留不太合适吧。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:顺便把手机递给明智君。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“嗯，那么新闻社……”佐佐木重拾起被明智打断的声音，“明智君的住宿已经安排好了，这点不必担心。嗯，那么新闻社见。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:手机中传来忙音。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“铃木君的家在哪呢？”我问。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:脚踢了两下地面把鞋子调整好，有些不好意思地开口。“我，我吗？我就住在公司附近的小房子里，租金很便宜，所以很小，很乱。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“那我们顺路呢，一起回去吧。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“嗯，今天一天确实跑了很多地方呢…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“走之前我们再去看看之前那位家属吧？总有一种心慌慌的感觉……”还是有些放心不下，向明智君提出了建议</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“说的是呢……我们再偷偷观望一会吧。”我思考了一下说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:于是没走多远的你们回到了那户人家门前。不知是否该谓之可惜，由于窗帘的遮挡，你们无法看到房间内部。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:.r1d2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:国际象棋黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：&lt;铃木香&gt;获得结果 1d2=3D2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“真是遗憾呢。”我说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“明智君在遗憾什么呀…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“嗯？？没什么，只是不能获得更多的情报，有些遗憾而已。”我愣了一下，解释道。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“希望那位女士能够平安。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“天色也不早了，我们还是早点回去吧。明天还是要再来的！”打了个哈欠</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“嗯，好好休息，明天也一起加油噢！希望今晚可以做个好梦呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们结束了一天的走访。回到新闻社时，天已经完全黑了。办公室里只剩下包括值班记者在内的十来个人。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >走进佐佐木的办公室时，他已经准备好了茶饮和小食，正等着你们回来：</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“大家辛苦了，今天一定很累吧。”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“这是为了追寻真相必须付出的努力呢，相比这个，今天看到的东西真是有些过于冲击了。”我坐下，吃东西。“不过我真的很饿了，非常感谢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“嗯，很好吃。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“确实很累呢…说起来，肚子也真的很饿了…”盯着那些食物</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我也拿点吃</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“请用！就是为二位准备的。”佐佐木将食物推向你们，“听起来是很艰辛的过程啊。好了，有什么重要的情报吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:饮品和食物都能算得上新鲜可口，多少消解了一些你们的疲惫。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:。log off 愚者的祈雨</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:“要继续讲述这个故事吗？我很乐意倾听下去。”他看起来倒是很有耐心的样子。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >故事</font>"愚者的祈雨"的记录已经继续开启，当前已记录文本1189</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:终于把嘴里的食物咽下去之后轻咳一声进行汇报。“我们今天去调查了案发现场以及通过警察的帮助，对尸体也进行了调查。还有对受害者家属的采访，只遇见了第六位受害者的家属。”于是把今天看到的听到的都大致跟佐佐木说了一通。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:佐佐木听着，有些惊奇地瞪大了眼睛：“竟然调查了尸体，还成功采访到了遗属，真是了不起！请问，现场和尸体有什么重要的情报信息吗？遗属又是怎么说的？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“现场和尸体只能用超自然这个词来概括了吧。尸体的形状和状态也很是诡异，像是3个问号拧在一起……抱歉，我这么说是不是太抽象了？铃木君有拍摄照片。”我顿了顿，“我们成功说上了话的那位遗属，她的状态……应该不能算好。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:佐佐木边听边皱起了眉头，转头向铃木：“铃木君，照片方便让我看一下吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我将女人说过的话大致转述出来。“现场我们还发现了一张行车记录仪的SD卡，看了两眼就自己坏掉了。”我将sd卡拿出来放在桌上。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“好的，在这里。”从背包里掏出自己的相机调出之前拍摄的照片递给佐佐木</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:由于屑kp的失误，铃木在此补过一个摄影吧。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:.ra 摄影</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的"摄影"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D18/50 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >现在正是扭转局势的机会哦。（困难成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“那个行车记录仪的内容，说出来怕是会被当做疯子吧。”我将行车记录仪拍到的内容向佐佐木描述了一遍。“这起案件怕是个邪教，甚至非人因素沾边了。再调查下去不一定能抓到实在的嫌犯，倒是可能小命不保了。”我流露出退意。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:佐佐木接过照片，堪堪扫了一眼，面色就变得煞白。“铃木君的摄影水平又精进了呢。”他几乎可以说是强撑着才将照片递回给你，“的确非常符合‘超自然’的说法……我不太确定这样的照片是否能用于报道，你先收着好了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:接过照片用担忧的眼神看了看佐佐木又看了看想退出的明智。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“SD卡啊……”听了明智之言，看过照片的佐佐木流露出担忧的神色，但还是将SD卡插入了自己的电脑，“这次案件的取材的确非常危险，但身为记者的我实在不能坐视不管。当然，明智君如果有自己的考虑，我也不会勉强你……咦，这怎么只有沙尘暴的影像？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“说起来，你们之前提到了警察的帮助吧……你们是怎么取得警方帮助的？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“哦…就是，走进去，然后说我们是调查雨人的…这样。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:明智不语，只是一味的喝茶。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“是、是这样吗？莫非手续之类的去繁从简了，又或者审核手续的工作人员们效率比以前高了很多？虽然有时警方是会协助记者工作啦，但一天内完成这么多安排还真是让我有些惊讶。”佐佐木有些疑惑，但还是表露出对你们取材成果的赞叹。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:吃上神饭了</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“都是多亏了有明智君，我一个人的话都不知道能完成什么呢。那个储存卡，在播放完我们所看到的内容后似乎就一直在循环沙尘暴了，很奇怪呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“竟然是这样，真的很奇怪呢……”佐佐木将SD卡取出，思考了一下，接着询问：“对了，从警方那边，你们有了解到案件细节和进展的信息吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“警方那边现在正在寻找雨人的据点，已经有大致的方位了，就在加祸市的东部。我和铃木君打算明天去搜查。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“加祸市的东部啊。嗯……范围有点大呢，不过有了方向就是一件值得庆幸的事了。对于具体的搜查地点，你们已经有头绪了吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“暂时还没有，不过我初步判断出了那个团体的特征，身穿黄色雨衣。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“嗯？明智君认为雨人是一个犯罪团伙吗？黄色雨衣的角度也让我觉得有些意外，有点好奇是怎么推断出的呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“对于地点没有头绪的话，要不要试着运用直觉？我们可以先思考可疑的地方，今晚把调查地点和路线拟定一下。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“实不相瞒，一天下来我听到了太多关于黄色衣服的信息了……我观察遗体的时候好像还听到遗体跟我说‘黄衣之主’什么的……不过，黄衣之主和黄色雨衣肯定不是一回事啦。”我笑着解释。“在车站的时候有听到过关于7-8个穿着黄色雨衣的人的情报哦，感到有些奇怪所以记住了。以及坏掉的那段录像里，也有出现过黄色衣服的身影。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“原来如此，我明白了。二位的调查似乎已经深入到一定程度了。”佐佐木理解地点点头。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“运用直觉嘛……根据我的经验，我倒是觉得工业区之类人迹罕至的地方很适合作为类似于邪教团体的据点。”我思考了一会，说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:想让pc而非pl运用直觉的话，请进行一个灵感吧。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra灵感</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的"灵感"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D61/80 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >浑身上下到处都是破绽呢，趁机解决掉吧。（成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:.ra 灵感</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的"灵感"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D91/50 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;，你敢倒下我就杀了你！（失败）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智这样说着，逐渐感到一种似曾相识的气味再度充盈鼻腔内——在案发现场闻到的，近似于工厂润滑油的气味。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“工业区么。据我所知，东部的确有一座所有者不明的废弃工厂，这样一看大概可以列为怀疑对象之一吧？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“除此以外可能另外有些可疑的地方，但我不知道具体信息，也许需要实地查看了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“我估计工业区的调查差不多会占用一天时间，那么稍后我为你们规划一些省时的路线，再把整理好的调查计划……”佐佐木停顿了一下，看向明智，“明智君，你之前……你还有意继续委托吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我个人的正义不允许我放弃追求真相……但是佐佐木先生如果愿意给我一些报酬的话，我可能会很高兴的。”我说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“谢谢你！完成了委托后，我会尽力不在报酬上亏待你们的。”佐佐木大受感动，并决定后付。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:.log off 愚者的祈雨</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:“要继续讲述这个故事吗？我很乐意倾听下去。”他看起来倒是很有耐心的样子。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >故事</font>"愚者的祈雨"的记录已经继续开启，当前已记录文本1350</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“那么，规划完后我这边就把整理好的调查计划发给两位！讨论了这么久，已经很晚了，今晚大家就先回去休息？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“好的。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“好的，辛苦佐佐木先生了，也辛苦明智君了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“明智君，我帮你预订好了酒店，就在附近。你在前台出示证件就可以了。”佐佐木将酒店的名片递给明智，开始整理食物容器，“今天辛苦了，回去的路上请多加小心。明天也多多关照了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“请多关照。”我接下名片。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:离开新闻社时，已经是八点了。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:我要回自己家洗刷刷休息整理照片和记录今天的日记</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:。rd2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;KP&gt;想要查看的结果吗？……调查出来的成果大概是这样d2=3D1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我决定趁早睡觉。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:那么铃木这么做了。虽然白天的所见所闻有些骇人，手中的照片也略显惊悚，但写着日记，你逐渐感到充实且平静。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智打算这么做，直接前往酒店，入住了房间。你发现房间内的书桌上放着一本黑色小书，仅有封面写着名字——黄衣之王。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:联想到白天出现的“幻觉”，我纠结再三，决定看一下。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:那是一部诗剧。仿佛是某个噩梦的碎片，支离破碎、模糊不清，却又带着一种无法抗拒的魅力，深深地吸引着继续阅读的明智，令你难以自拔。随着故事推进，一种可怕的存在终于登场。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >这个存在拥有无数触手，身披由自身鳞片编织的⻩色长袍，宛如邪恶的化身。而象征⻩⾐之王的</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“⻩印”不仅是对王的绝对臣服的标志，更是传播疯狂与腐化的诅咒源泉。这个印记的形状，与受害者的模样完全吻合。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-