0font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >尽管先前向佐佐木表示过已经做好心里建设，但临近目的地的此时，你才终于感到自己鼓起了足够直面雨人的勇气</font><font face=3D"宋体" >——即使只是一种可能性。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:之后的技能检定中，铃木可以获得一次+10的调整值。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们来到了佐佐木标出的第一处地点，东部工业区内的一间废弃工厂。一辆警车停在工厂前面，车内并没有人。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >工厂外布满了锈迹和涂鸦，显然已被遗弃许久。所有窗户都从内部被木板封死，前方的防火卷帘门满是锈蚀，底部距地面有一丝空隙。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“警车…？警察比我们先到了吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“似乎并没看到人呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:看了看卷帘门下面。“…警察是从这进去的吗？”面色有些为难</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:铃木估量了一下，缝隙的大小的确能让一个中等身形的人通过。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >内部漆黑一片。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:。rd2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:国际象棋黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：&lt;铃木香&gt;获得结果 d2=3D2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“总有种不好的预感呢…明智君能替我打一下手电吗，我看看我能不能钻过去。”蹲下来看看自己能不能过去。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“当然可以。”我拿出手电筒蹲下来帮铃木照明。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:铃木顺利而平缓地钻了过去。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我叹了口气。“那么我也……”虽然我在心里非常不想弄脏自己的衬衫，但我不得不也跟随铃木爬进去。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:。rd</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:国际象棋黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：&lt;铃木香&gt;获得结果 D100=3D31</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智也爬进了工厂内。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >靠着手电光，你们看见前方有一个左向转角。转角右侧的墙壁嵌着一扇门。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“就这样进来了呢，感觉似乎没有别的路了。”拍拍身上的灰站了起来，从包里掏出弹簧刀攥在手里向转角走去。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我们走吧。”我小声说，跟在铃木的右后方。偷偷从手提箱内拿出手枪放在裤子口袋里。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们走向转角，那扇门逐渐清晰，上方装有一块褪色的牌子，能辨认出“办公室”的字样。在转角尽头，这扇门对面，是一道长长的走廊。面对走廊，你们的左手侧也有两扇门，比第一扇门小一些。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我们按照顺序来吧，先去离我们最近的。”我朝左手边的一扇门抬了抬下巴，轻声说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“好。”深吸一口气给自己暗自加油了一番终于鼓足勇气想要打开左手边的门。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:随着你们靠近，一种腐臭的气息逐渐渗入你们的鼻腔。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“这股味道……”我感觉味道有些熟悉，皱了皱眉。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们打开了最近的一扇门。房间内部有十个左右的储物柜，以及两把长椅。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智感觉这有点像尸体腐败的味道。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:萌生了退意“…要不，要不我们再打开一下另一扇门看看？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“也可以。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:反正我有枪。我这么在心里安慰着自己。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们轻轻关上这扇门，打开了邻近的一扇。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >内部是一样的配置，但对称着进行了摆放。空气中仍然弥漫着那种气味，你们说不清楚那种味道是减淡了还是更浓郁了。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“两边都一样啊…总感觉，很像太平间呢。”试图开玩笑无能</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“要进行搜查吗？”我问</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“可能会看到尸体噢。”我提醒道。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:回忆起昨天见到的尸体面色苍白“难道，都会是我们见过的那个样子的吗…另一个房间会有尸体吗…”后退了一步离开了房间站在走廊上眼神游移</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:走廊的另一头浸没在黑暗之中。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“没做好心理准备的话……我们可以先去看一眼‘办公室’。”我提议道。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“呜呜明明在佐佐木先生面前立下了豪言壮志说做好了心理准备，结果现在却……不行，先从我能做到的做起！走吧，我们去看办公室！”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们关上门后折返，打开了办公室的门。借着手电筒的光，可以看见这是一间摆放有办公桌和资料架的普通办公室。房间显然被人为地翻乱过。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:办公室内部也有一扇门。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“是警察已经调查过了吗……？可是不应该啊，现场怎么会这么混乱。”我皱起眉。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“看上去不像是正式的出警…不管怎么说，要是能遇上就可以算是帮手吧”看看办公桌上有没有什么东西</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:那么我警惕着门外的情况。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:桌面上散落着一些发霉的物质，铃木认为它们曾是名为便当、面包、罐头的物品。这些剩饭的腐败程度不同，但少说也有两三个月了。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:铃木过侦查。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:。ra 侦查</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的"侦查"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D91/55 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >你是在害怕吗？啧，表现的真没出息。（失败）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“铃木君，有什么发现吗？”我观察到附近没有人，我们不用担心立刻被发现后，回过头来问铃木。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:的确，刚刚守望时，明智发现附近相当安静。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“我看到桌上只有一些过期食物，感觉这里已经有好几个月没人生活过了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“这样啊……”我看向办公室内的另一扇门。“那么这扇门会有什么作用呢？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:说着我靠近了这扇门，试图听门后有没有动静。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我再摸摸资料架</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智只能听到铃木翻动资料架的微小声音。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:以我目前的状态，贸然搜查是不理智的。所以我决定帮助铃木摸索。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:资料架上零星散落着一些残缺破旧的废纸。铃木在其中找到了一份工厂的平面图。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们发现锅炉房的位置标记了一个“X”符号。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:那么明智也走向混乱堆着发霉剩饭的办公桌。你觉得这些剩饭看起来与办公室有些违和。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智过侦查。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra侦查</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的"侦查"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D1/80 一口气击溃他们！（大成功）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智在食物堆中发现了一台收音机盒式录音机。录音机里放着一盘磁带，磁带盘上写着“教主音声”。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“这个东西…会和存储卡一样是一次性的吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我不知道……很有可能呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我顿了一下说。“总之，不能轻易播放这个……”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“…是，是呢…可是，万一有什么线索…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我深吸了一口气。“好吧。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智按下了播放键，陌生的男人声音徐徐传来：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“我们的一切皆属于伟大的主。静下心来，聆听祂的声音，仰望星空，感受风的拂过，心怀感激，因为我们是祂的产物。即便肉体朽坏，我们的灵魂也将通过祭坛、升往那黑哈里湖，成为主的眷属，与祂共享永恒的时光。不要惧怕死亡，也不要拒绝疯狂，因为主的回应会降临，祂会满足我们的愿望。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:都过一个灵感吧。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra灵感</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的"灵感"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D3/80 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >把敌人折磨到死</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……！（极难成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:.ra 灵感</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的"灵感"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D83/50 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >抱歉，晕眩状态</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……敌人的位置在……？（失败）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智突然意识到，这个声音很可能来自于两个月前被目击过的那个神秘集体。他们似乎试图召唤自己崇拜的神祇降临此地，借此获得不老不死的恩赐。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:.log off愚者的祈雨</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:“要继续讲述这个故事吗？我很乐意倾听下去。”他看起来倒是很有耐心的样子。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >故事</font>"愚者的祈雨"的记录已经继续开启，当前已记录文本2231</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“所以…那位家属所说的就是这个意思吗？什么不老不死啊，这不是完全在骗人吗。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“这就是邪教啊，无论是否拥有这种能力，重要的是教徒的深信不疑……”我面色有些凝重。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“嘛……虽然我是不相信这些的，至少目前为止是这样。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“这样下去肯定还会有源源不断的人被骗然后失去生命的。可是我们要怎样阻止呢…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“交给警方吧？掌握了这个证据，我觉得我们可以报警了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“报…报警吗，警车不是已经在门口了吗”那种语气</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“可是只有一辆……如果要逮捕邪教组织的话恐怕有些缺乏人手。保险一点总不会错？顺便也可以问一下出警察的情况”我皱了皱眉。“而且完全没听到警察的动静啊……”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“嗯，也是呢。不愧是明智君，想得好周到！就是希望这个警察不要出事啊…”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:于是我拨通了报警电话。试图说明现在的情况并询问出警状况。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:一个陌生的声音接了这通电话。他表示警察们在好好守护市民的安全，虽然因工作要求不能告诉你出警状况，但如果你有困难，可以派遣警力来帮助你。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“或许我可以直接问田中警官？”没得到什么有用的线索，我提议。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我认为这么做并没有什么损失，而且想到了和田中的交易，决定给田中打电话。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“田中警官，呃，署里有很多位田中警官。如果你们认识，不如直接打那位的私人电话吧？”对面似乎在评估这是否是一通恶作剧电话。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:看明智君的问话也决定打电话给田中先生，把拨打电话的界面在明智君面前晃了晃。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:那么我等着铃木和田中对话。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:铃木拨打了电话。没有人接听。等待了一段时间后，呼叫自动结束了。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“……田中先生不接电话。我有一些不好的预感……”挂了电话，紧张地来回踱步，思考下一步该做什么，停在了办公室里面的那扇门前，“那我们就打开这扇门看看吧？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:原本想回看上去更安全的更衣室搜查的我把话咽了回去。“也好。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们打开这扇门，大致看到门后是配备了用于材料加工的工作台和各种设备的宽敞空间。空气中充斥着润滑油和铁锈的气味，隐隐混杂着一股与在更衣室门口闻见味道近似的腐臭。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“没有看到警察啊……”我心里越发不安。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“这股味道……必须得报警了。”我对铃木说。“铃木君，用你的手机报警吧。就说这个工厂里发现了尸体。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“好，我来打吧。”再次打开手机拨通报警电话，深呼吸几次作出害怕的声音，“是，是警察吗？我在东部地区的废弃工厂里发现了尸体…！你们快过来看看吧！”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“尸体？”对面的声音变得有些紧张，也许他在想——除了雨人外，加祸市还有其他杀人犯吗？</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >“收到了，女士，请不要惊慌。请问发现尸体的具体位置是？”警察向铃木确认了具体位置后，继续确认现场情况，“尸体状况是怎样的？您处于危险中吗？身边是否有其他人？请务必确保自身的安全，我们马上派警员来查看情况。”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“发现了扭曲的人体残肢……”我结合之前看到的尸体和现场的情况随口编了一个，小声提醒铃木。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“具体位置……就说是加工厂和锅炉房内吧。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“尸体…尸体散发了很臭的味道，我不敢看它……看上去像被扭曲了一样，完全不像人类！就在这个工厂的加工厂里面，你们赶快来吧！我和我的一个同伴一起在这里面。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“了解了……女士，您身边有危险人物吗？感谢您报告情况，如果您处于安全状态的话，希望您和您的同伴能在此时的地点等待我们的警员来，稍后可能还需要你们配合工作。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“嗯，我会的。”挂了电话问明智，“我们现在就去看看里面吗？死了也还有警察给我们收尸呢。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我苦中作乐地噗嗤笑了一下。“好的，铃木君。我殿后。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:走进室内，你们发现地面上有五个很大的黑色人形污渍。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:过侦查。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:.ra 侦查</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;铃木香&gt;的"侦查"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D60/55 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >竟然没中！你给我看清楚好吗，</font>&lt;铃木香&gt;!（失败）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra 侦查</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0