t-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >很碍眼啊</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……你。快些消失吧。（成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:这具尸体形状可怖，你的确不想多看一眼。但身为记者对真相的追求，又促使你再次将目光转向它。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你发现雨衣之下，死者的双手紧握着一张纸条。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我试图眯着眼睛捂住鼻子单手去拿纸条</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你费了点力气，才将纸条从那双僵硬而腐朽的手中较为完整地取出。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:纸条上的文字模糊不清难以辨认，看起来像是在黑暗中匆忙书写的：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >“我们错了。做出了无法挽回的事。没有人预料到会变成这样。我们不该渴望永生，也不该追求不老不死。我们从未听说过会变成那副模样。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >我想逃，可是哪里也逃不出去。那家伙在门外盯着我，注视着我们这些亵渎者。疯狂的主不宽恕我们。这个城市已经成了祭坛，我们哪里也躲不开。原本为万一准备好的护身符，也不知道哪里去了。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >对不起。对不起。对不起。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >请原谅作为愚者的我。</font><font face=3D"宋体" >”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:把纸条也拿给明智君看。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我接过纸条读了一遍。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“看来追求永生确实是不可能的啊。像是完全落入了邪教的陷阱……”我说。“以及这个护身符，如果知道在哪里就好了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:。log off 愚者的祈雨</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:“要继续讲述这个故事吗？我很乐意倾听下去。”他看起来倒是很有耐心的样子。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >故事</font>"愚者的祈雨"的记录已经继续开启，当前已记录文本2596</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“还有一件更衣室……”我有些心有余悸</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“呼…总之，应该也是尸体吧。走吧，我们去看看。”走向男更衣室</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:做好了心理准备，你们在男更衣室搜查了一圈。不知该失望还是庆幸，男更衣室的储物柜空空如也，并没有不妙的东西。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“竟然没有奇怪的东西呢，太好了。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“按照线路…接下来先去仓库，最后再去锅炉房吧。”我说，“走吧？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“走吧！”扫了两眼确认没有什么落下的线索就跟随明智君出门了</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们进入了工厂的仓库。散落在地上的废料显然曾被使用过，每走一步都能听见嘎嘎作响的脚步声。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我摸索摸索看看有没有什么除了废料之外的东西</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:一起过一个幸运，铃木再过一个侦查吧。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal 