pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.ra聆听</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的"聆听"检定结果为: 国际象棋的黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >D100=3D17/80 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >几乎全是杂兵呢，照这个势头下去也要继续取胜。（困难成功）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们分辨出，那杂乱的声音似乎是由众多人的谈话声混杂而成。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那我悄咪咪地走两步看看，再仔细听听</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:杂乱的声音依旧存在于遥远的某处，你听不清确切的内容。与此同时，被注视的不安感也持续萦绕在你心中。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“…好奇怪啊，可是都到这一步了。只能慢慢地往里面走了。”握紧手里的木棍开始往深处轻轻地走</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:那么我也跟在她身后。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:虽然不安感依旧，但一路上并没有异常状况，你们走到了锅炉房的尽头。此处墙壁被切割成正方形，通道向深处延伸。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >这是地图上没有标记的区域，杂音似乎是由通道深处传来的。但当你们站在入口时，那声音戛然而止。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“明智君，要走进这个通道吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“事到如今如果我说别进去你也不会同意吧。”我无奈地说。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:通道漫长，去向不明。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“…说不定真的要找人收尸了，这一切都远远超出了我的预期…可是走到这一步然后回去，即使是我也做不到了呢。要是明智君感到害怕了的话也可以就在这里等我呀。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“我怎么可能害怕呢？”我露出笑容。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:那么我向通道里走去</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:我跟随她。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:你们毅然决然地迈开了前进的步伐。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:穿越了漫长而黑暗的通道，尽头是某个空间。这片空间，仿佛没有天花板和四壁，漆黑的虚空无边无际，唯独中央伫立着一座由矿石雕琢而成的王座。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >满地漫着水。这里的水既不温暖也不寒冷，悄然浸湿了你们的双脚。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:我踩了踩地上的水，奇怪的感觉让我有些摸不着头脑。我下意识地往王座那边走近了些想观察一下。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:铃木踩了踩地下的水，突然发现水面中映出了一个城市的倒影。从近乎神明的视角俯瞰，那座城市正是加祸市——雨中的加祸市。突然之间你意识到，这片异空间与加祸市之间存在某种不可见的连接。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:明智静滞原地，看着铃木走向王座。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >铃木看见了用未知矿石雕刻而成的一个王座，那矿石美得仿佛不属于人世间。靠背的中央雕刻着⻩印，整座王座散发出一种异样的气息，仅仅凝视它就让你不由自主地感到一阵寒意。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:原本不该存在的孩童声，带着一种怪异的回响在空气中回荡。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >“呐，你知道雨人吗？”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >从日常中割裂开来的，关于雨人的低语声。声音响起的同时，脚下的水面也悄然泛起波纹。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >雨人。雨人。雨人。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >无数的声音交织，渐渐地从十个、百个、千个，变得越来越多，男女老少的声音交替回响。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >水面波纹渐起，眼前的景象如同在夜雨中的湖泊。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >当这一切达到顶极点时，所有的声音瞬息之间停止，取而代之的是两道人声。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:沉稳中略带青涩的少年的声音：“今天的天气很好呢，看来是不会有雨人作案了，理论上来说的话。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >“雨人到底为什么会挑选这样的时间作案呢…？”疑惑的女声，下一刻呈现出某种思索与向往，“……如果能够调查出雨人的真面目，能够阻止更多的人死去，那么也能证明自己是有用的吧？”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >声音停顿了一会儿，模糊的嘈杂声响起了片刻，又迅速熄灭。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >“见到雨人之后…我们也会被赋予永恒的生命吗？”女声继续说着，这次声音中似乎带着畏惧。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >少年的声音穿插了进来：</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“警方那边现在正在寻找雨人的据点，已经有大致的方位了……”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >最后，女性的声音在工厂中轻轻回响：</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“……能够确认这里应该就是雨人的据点了么……”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:随着这最后一句话的落下，听见无数呼声的某物在王座中显现。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >那是一个身穿⻩色长袍、约有</font>2米高的人形怪物。祂佩戴着一张令人联想到死亡的苍白面具，</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >悠然地坐在王座中。那看似是⻩色长袍的东西，其实是触手，从那怪异的身体上伸展出来。腐烂与污秽的气息开始在周围弥漫，水面开始被王的存在所染黑。祂那既恐怖又庄严的身影让你们意识到了灭亡的降临，但没有人能将目光移开。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:亲眼见到旧日支配者哈斯塔的化身『⻩⾐之王』显现，sc1/1d8。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.sc1/1d8</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的理智检定:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >d100=3D64/35 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >说实话我讨厌你（失败）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >理智变化</font>: 35 &#10159; 33 (扣除1d8=3D2点)</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >看起来</font>&lt;骰子&gt;的状态似乎有些不对，需要治疗恢复。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=