:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >理智变化</font>: 72 &#10159; 71 (扣除1=3D1点)如果被这点小事都吓倒了的话，也就没办法继续攻陷宫殿了。话说到这里，你可不要拖我后腿哦？</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.sc0/1d2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:&lt;骰子&gt;的理智检定:</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >d100=3D57/33 </span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >是绝望状态？</font><font face=3D"宋体" >……放任不管的话会很危险（失败）</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >理智变化</font>: 33 &#10159; 32 (扣除1d2=3D1点)</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:42.7500pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >你还好吗？看起来需要纸扇恢复的样子，赶紧醒来吧。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“谢、谢谢你，铃木，我、好像知道了。”佐佐木面色苍白，走到自动饮水机旁给你们一人倒了一杯水。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:外面依旧下着雨。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >将两杯水放在你们面前，佐佐木深吸了一口气：</font><font face=3D"宋体" >“那么，我想我们应该做出一个选择——是否该公开这件事的真相？”</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“是将雨男的真相公之于众，还是……保持沉默？这个决定将带来什么后果，我也无法预料……但我觉得，既然我们已经揭开了这个真相，就应该对它负责。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“你们的想法……能告诉我吗？”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:.r1d2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(195,43,43);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;骰子&gt;:国际象棋黑白棋盘上，白棋挪动了一步：&lt;骰子&gt;获得结果 1d2=3D1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(144,114,85);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;明智吾郎&gt;:“这样的真相……不知道还能不能获得悬赏金呢。总不能让我们的努力白费，让真相蒙尘吧？”我提出了我的想法。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“我承诺的报酬，肯定会为你们兑现。警方那边……我不知道，毕竟是这种超出认知的真相……”佐佐木思索着，看向铃木，“铃木君也经历了很多吧……你更倾向于公开真相，还是……”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(95,63,132);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;铃木香&gt;:“我…我不知道。如果我没参与调查的话，肯定希望知道真相。可是这种真相，那种无法理解的事物，让大众得知以后会发生什么，我不知道……”咬了咬下嘴唇，挣扎了一会还是接着说，“但是我想，报道事实是我应该做的，人群应该知道真相。”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:“的确，这是一个很艰难的选择啊。”佐佐木语毕，你们陷入一阵沉默。忽然，他似乎下定了决心：“我知道了，既然亲自调查的你们这么说的话……我们这就做一篇报道，把真相展示给公众看吧。首先，需要你们收集的材料……”</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:虽然很遗憾，没有适合报道的图片材料，但你们很快将走访留下的笔录整理好，做出了一篇报道。在佐佐木的努力下，除了临时加入明天的日报，这篇令人丝毫没有真实感觉的报道，在新闻社的互联网账号上得到了今日的即时推送。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >雨人的真相终于在阳光下暴露无遗。⻩⾐之王的恐怖透过文字、语言甚至互联网不断扩散。你们履行了作为知情者的责任，内心不知为何涌上一股异样的成就感。就在这时，雨声戛然而止，四周突然陷入一片死寂。几秒钟后，你们逐渐放松了紧绷的神经，意识开始模糊，</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >慢慢陷入了黑暗。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:第二天清晨，透过办公室窗户洒下的阳光中，你们缓缓醒来。打开手机时，你们忽然发现，关于雨人的所有话题和信息似乎都消失了。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >你们曾经发表的报道了无痕迹，其他曾经热衷于报道雨人的媒体，也再没有提及过他。没有人再提起这个名字，仿佛关于雨人的一切记忆都被彻底抹去。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >因为余有疑团，明智在加祸市停留了几天。几天后，你们逐渐意识到，加祸市与⻩⾐之王之间的联系已被某种强大的力量彻底切断。曾经的废弃工厂被彻底拆除，而你们的账户中也莫名其妙地多了一笔</font>600万日元的款项。这既像是奖励，又像是警告。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3DMsoNormal  style=3D"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&lt;KP&gt;:随着愚者的祈雨逐渐平息，加祸市恢复了平静。你们接受了佐佐木的谢礼，而关于雨人的调查，也在这一刻宣告结束。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >走出新闻社，你们看见加祸市罕见的六月晴空</font><font face=3D"宋体" >——如洗净尘埃般的湛蓝天空。然而，街头大屏幕上正在播放的失踪人员信息却让你们不禁停下了脚步。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >画面中冷漠地列出了一系列失踪者的照片和名字。其中，⽥中宗介赫然在列。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;=20text-indent:33.7000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(102,144,198);=20font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face=3D"宋体" >……刹那间，周围的喧嚣仿佛骤然消失，取而代之的是一阵耳鸣般的沉默，仿佛从某个隐秘的角落传来一声低语。</font></span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;=20mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp  style=3D"margin-top: